              &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
      h3 使用栅格(Using Grid)
      p 当然，你可以把按钮放在任何你想放的位置。比如放在 <a href="grid.html">栅格</a> 中:
      pre
        code
          | &lt;div class="row"&gt;
          |   &lt;div class="col-50"&gt;
          |     &lt;a href="#" class="button button-big button-red"&gt;Cancel&lt;/a&gt;
          |   &lt;/div&gt;
          |   &lt;div class="col-50"&gt;
          |     &lt;a href="#" class="button button-big button-green"&gt;Submit&lt;/a&gt;
          |   &lt;/div&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;          
      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/buttons-material.html") Material Theme Buttons
      h3 Usual/Flat Buttons
      p As in iOS Theme just add button class to any link or button input:
      pre
        code
          | &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="button"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          | &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="button"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;          
      h3 Buttons Row
      p Just wrap buttons with element with <code>buttons-row</code> class:
      pre
        code
          | &lt;p class="buttons-row"&gt;
          |   &lt;a href="#" class="button"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;
          |   &lt;a href="#" class="button"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;
          | &lt;/p&gt;          
      h3 Raised Buttons
      p Add <code>button-raised</code> class to button:
      pre
        code
          | &lt;p class="buttons-row"&gt;
          |   &lt;a href="#" class="button button-raised"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;
          |   &lt;a href="#" class="button button-raised"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;
          |   &lt;a href="#" class="button button-raised"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;
          | &lt;/p&gt;          
      h3 Raised Fill Buttons
      p Add <code>button-fill</code> class to button:
